North Korea ’s military raised its
alert status since the death of leader  Kim Jong Il , South Korean
Defense Minister Kim Kwan Jin told a parliament committee in
 Seoul  today. There have been no signs of provocation from the
North, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
